109// BandParameters ::= CHOICE
110struct band_params_c {
111 struct eutra_s_ {
112 bool ca_bw_class_dl_eutra_present = false;
113 bool ca_bw_class_ul_eutra_present = false;
114 uint16_t band_eutra = 1;
115 ca_bw_class_eutra_e ca_bw_class_dl_eutra;
116 ca_bw_class_eutra_e ca_bw_class_ul_eutra;
117 };
118 struct nr_s_ {
119 bool ca_bw_class_dl_nr_present = false;
120 bool ca_bw_class_ul_nr_present = false;
121 uint16_t band_nr = 1;
122 ca_bw_class_nr_e ca_bw_class_dl_nr;
123 ca_bw_class_nr_e ca_bw_class_ul_nr;
124 };
125 struct types_opts {
126 enum options { eutra, nr, nulltype } value;
127
128 const char* to_string() const;
129 };
130 using types = enumerated<types_opts>;
131
132 // choice methods
133 band_params_c() = default;
134 band_params_c(const band_params_c& other);
135 band_params_c& operator=(const band_params_c& other);
136 ~band_params_c() { destroy_(); }
137 void set(types::options e = types::nulltype);
138 types type() const { return type_; }
139 SRSASN_CODE pack(bit_ref& bref) const;
140 SRSASN_CODE unpack(cbit_ref& bref);
141 void to_json(json_writer& j) const;
142 // getters
143 eutra_s_& eutra()
144 {
145 assert_choice_type(types::eutra, type_, "BandParameters");
146 return c.get<eutra_s_>();
147 }
148 nr_s_& nr()
149 {
150 assert_choice_type(types::nr, type_, "BandParameters");
151 return c.get<nr_s_>();
152 }
153 const eutra_s_& eutra() const
154 {
155 assert_choice_type(types::eutra, type_, "BandParameters");
156 return c.get<eutra_s_>();
157 }
158 const nr_s_& nr() const
159 {
160 assert_choice_type(types::nr, type_, "BandParameters");
161 return c.get<nr_s_>();
162 }
163 eutra_s_& set_eutra();
164 nr_s_& set_nr();
165
166private:
167 types type_;
168 choice_buffer_t<eutra_s_, nr_s_> c;
169
170 void destroy_();
171};
